  "text": "Each use case was evaluated using an 8-item UX questionnaire (UEQ-S, [CITATION_1] ) and one-item trust and paternalism scales, accompanied by a short semi-structured interview 3 , after they had experienced the application. In the end, participants ranked the use case clusters according to their preferences and had the chance to discuss their most and least favorite functionalities.",
